Class OIDCBackChannelAuthCodeCache

  • public class OIDCBackChannelAuthCodeCache
extends org.wso2.carbon.identity.application.common.cache.BaseCache<OIDCBackChannelAuthCodeCacheKey,OIDCBackChannelAuthCodeCacheEntry>
